                <h1>Protest breaks out after UNC leaders recommend $5.3 million facility to house Silent Sam</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/61b80c88-29b6-46a1-aee4-7601ba0deb4f.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

